---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="AutoPilot Sites privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <div class="container-narrow about-section">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: January 2025</em></p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect minimal information to improve our website and content:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> Anonymous page view data (pages visited, time on site, referring URLs)</li>
      <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use cookies for basic analytics and affiliate link tracking</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To improve our website and content</li>
      <li>To track affiliate referrals (no personal data is shared with affiliate partners)</li>
      <li>To understand which tools and topics our readers find most valuable</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Affiliate networks:</strong> When you click an affiliate link, the network may set a cookie to track the referral</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Anonymous analytics to understand site usage patterns</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You can opt out of analytics cookies through your browser settings. You have the right to request deletion of any personal data we may hold about you.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related inquiries: <a href="mailto:privacy@autopilotsites.ai">privacy@autopilotsites.ai</a></p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>